爱心魔王FHC 发表于 2019-11-29 23:52
用tp不要用Motion
我大概摸出方法了，需要分别判定26类相对位置，且单坐标优先级高于双坐标，双坐标高于三坐标。
另外，就特定实体是否在水中也需要判定。

/scoreboard players tag @e remove onwater
/execute @a ~ ~ ~ execute @e[x=~,y=~,z=~,r=32] ~ ~ ~ detect ~ ~ ~ minecraft:water * scoreboard players tag @s add onwater
/execute @a ~ ~ ~ execute @e[x=~,y=~,z=~,r=32] ~ ~ ~ detect ~ ~1 ~ minecraft:water * scoreboard players tag @s add onwater

/scoreboard players tag @e[tag=a] remove behave_approach
/execute @e[tag=a] ~ ~ ~ scoreboard players tag @s[tag=onwater] add behave_approach

/execute @a ~ ~ ~ execute @e[tag=a,x=~,y=~,z=~,dx=20,dy=20,dz=20] ~ ~ ~ entitydata @s[tag=behave_approach] {Motion:[-0.3d,-0.3d,-0.3d]}
/execute @a ~ ~ ~ execute @e[tag=a,x=~,y=~,z=~,dx=20,dy=-20,dz=20] ~ ~ ~ entitydata @s[tag=behave_approach] {Motion:[-0.3d,0.3d,-0.3d]}
